OL,3,C'You can't just forget about it': WWII
OL,4,Cchild prisoners on life in Chinese
OL,5,Ccamps
OL,7,FOnce two children imprisoned in war,
OL,8,Fnow two friends who have so much to
OL,9,Fcatch up on.
OL,11,FIan was just ten years old when he and
OL,12,Fhis family were taken by Japanese
OL,13,Ftroops to Lunghua camp in China.
OL,15,FKatherine was 11 months old. She was
OL,16,Ftaken along with her parents and
OL,17,Fyounger brother to Weihsien camp.
OL,19,FThey were two of an estimated 40,000
OL,20,Fchildren locked away in East Asia
OL,21,Fduring World War II.
