OL,3,C'You can't just forget about it': WWII
OL,4,Cchild prisoners on life in Chinese
OL,5,Ccamps
OL,7,FIn 1945 after America dropped two
OL,8,Fatomic bombs on Nagasaki and
OL,9,FHiroshima, Japan surrendered and the
OL,10,Fwar officially ended.
OL,12,FIan described what happened when the
OL,13,FAmericans came.
OL,15,F"They rolled into the camp and they
OL,16,Fmade a sumptuous meal for us that
OL,17,Fnight. Then they played us a film, a
OL,18,Ftechnicoloured film which I hadn't
OL,19,Fseen for six years, that was fantastic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
