OL,3,C'You can't just forget about it': WWII
OL,4,Cchild prisoners on life in Chinese
OL,5,Ccamps
OL,7,F"I'll never forget walking out of the
OL,8,Fcamp and looking back into the camp
OL,9,Fwhere we'd been stuck for three years.
OL,10,FI really did feel free, that was
OL,11,Famazing."
OL,13,FFor Katherine it's always been hard to
OL,14,Faccept she was liberated after the
OL,15,Fbombs landed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
