OL,3,C'You can't just forget about it': WWII
OL,4,Cchild prisoners on life in Chinese
OL,5,Ccamps
OL,7,F"How do you begin to think about the
OL,8,Fhorrors of Hiroshima and Nagasaki in
OL,9,Fcontext with your own freedom? It's
OL,10,Fvery hard but you can't say one life
OL,11,Fis more important than another life,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,FEighty years on for them it's never
OL,15,Fbeen more important to remember VJ day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
