OL,3,C'You can't just forget about it': WWII
OL,4,Cchild prisoners on life in Chinese
OL,5,Ccamps
OL,7,F"There was so much pain and so much
OL,8,Fbitterness, so much horror, you can't
OL,9,Fjust forget about it, it's important
OL,10,Fto remember and that people realise
OL,11,Fthat if you go to war like that people
OL,12,Fsuffer terribly," Ian said.
OL,14,FAs they said goodbye to each other,
OL,15,FIan and Katherine couldn't stop
OL,16,Ftalking.
OL,18,FTwo children silenced in the war with
OL,19,Fso much still to say.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
